OL,5, An expert panel set up to design an    
OL,6, investigation into institutions for    
OL,7, unmarried mothers in Northern Ireland  
OL,8, is to announce its findings on Tuesday.
OL,10,FThe devolved government committed to an
OL,11,Finvestigation earlier this year after  
OL,12,Fresearch into mother-and-baby homes and
OL,13,FMagdalene Laundries was published.     
OL,15,FWomen who were in the institutions have
OL,16,Fsaid they were detained against their  
OL,17,Fwill, forced into unpaid labour and    
OL,18,Fmade to give up babies for adoption.   
OL,20,FA UN committee called for an inquiry.  
